{
  "stem": "54.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They concentrate us in a place in ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And everybody grabbed something with him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I was by myself at that time, because I was working night shift.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And when I came home, my parents, were at work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I grabbed whatever I could.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were always ready with suitcases in the house, that we knew that one day, they going to take-- tell us to go, and that's it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So everybody had-- everyone of us, each member of the family had a packed suitcase.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I grabbed the suitcases, but how many could I take?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I took as many as I could.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We came out on the appell place, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were standing over there, until then they called the rest people from the factories.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They came home, because we didn't know what's going on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We didn't know they were going to send us out from the home.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So when we came-- when my parents came, so they joined me, and I had all the suitcases with me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because I had money there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We had money, we had jewelry, and everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And when stayed-- we stayed there on the appell place, they told us to leave all the suitcases in-- in a-- you know, in a place, a line, you know, in another-- in another spot, that we couldn't take with us anything.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Nothing whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So in this from there, my sister-- when my sister came, so she says, what are we going to do?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We're going to be without even for the next day, nothing to change.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So she risk her life, she ran out from the line, and she grabbed the suitcase.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But the suitcase was not mine, it was not hers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Probably was my parents'.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We couldn't wear my parents' clothes, we were children.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
